        A little bit about my journey and interests.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base-content text-left">
        <p>
          Hello there! I'm Nine from Thailand, currently studying at Triamudom
          Suksa School in Bangkok. I enjoy playing games, especially strategy,
          building, and co-op games. Some of my favorites include Stellaris,
          Cities: Skylines, Minecraft, and Overwatch, though I play many others
          as well.
        </p>
        <div class="divider my-4"></div>
        <p>
          I'm proficient in <span class="badge badge-primary">Python</span> and <span
            class="badge badge-secondary">JavaScript/TypeScript</span
          >, with these being the languages I'm most comfortable with.
          Currently, I'm working on my personal site/portfolio and the Saiko-Pet
          Discord bot.
        </p>
        <div class="divider my-4"></div>
        <p>
          In the future, I plan to offer services, so feel free to reach out and
          connect with me! I'm most active on Discord, so don't hesitate to drop
          me a message.
        </p>
